d 'POLISHPAPER': module to Generate a Structured Polishing Template for Academic Papers
d
d	The polishpaper command generates a structured text file
d containing a polishing template for academic	  papers. The
d template includes seven tasks designed to guide users through the
d manuscript revision process. 
d
d KW: text management
d
d Requires: Stata version 16
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260504
d
d Author: Wu LiangHai,  Anhui University of Technology
